translation.en: for not packing up and going home.
translation.es: por no empacar e irme a casa.

translation.en: Good news.
Doc's not gonna throw you a parade, but he agreed to try you out.
translation.es: Doc no te hará una fiesta de bienvenida, pero aceptó probarte.

translation.en: You start immediately.
Hope, you've already hired me.
Well, here's the thing.
I'm paying your salary, but it is his practice, so...
translation.es: yo pagaré tu sueldo, pero es su clínica. - Así que... - ¿Por qué no me lo dijiste?

translation.en: Why didn't you just tell me that?
translation.es: - Así que... - ¿Por qué no me lo dijiste?

translation.en: Honey, then you wouldn't have come, would you?
Like my father said to my mother at the altar,
translation.es: Como papá le dijo a mamá en el altar:

translation.en: You're already here, so let's make the best of it.
Well, I'm not staying in that shack another night.
translation.es: Bien, pero no me quedaré en esa choza.

translation.en: I gotta side with Mel on that one.
You stay out of this.
Do I need to remind you that we have a--
Oh, oh, I'm fully aware that we have a contract.
translation.es: Sé perfectamente que tenemos un contrato.

translation.en: Okay? I'm also aware that suitable housing was part of the deal,
translation.es: ¿De acuerdo? También sé que el trato incluía un alojamiento adecuado,

translation.en: so technically, you're in breach.
translation.es: así que, técnicamente, estás violando lo acordado.

translation.en: Which means the contract is null and void. I can leave whenever I want.
translation.es: Eso anula el contrato y puedo irme cuando quiera.

translation.en: - - Can you afford to have her leave?
translation.es: ¿Puedes darte el lujo de dejarla ir?

translation.en: No.
Well, why don't you get her a room at the Fitches'?
translation.es: ¿Y si le das un cuarto en el Fitches?

translation.en: I'll fix up the cabin. Ricky could help me.
I'm not made of money.
Hope, please don't poor- mouth to me.
translation.es: Hope, no te hagas la pobre conmigo.

translation.en: You and I both know you couldn't spend half of what you have if you tried.
translation.es: Sabemos que no alcanzarías a gastar ni la mitad de lo que tienes.

translation.en: You're offering an awful lot of yourself to help a complete stranger.
translation.es: Estás ofreciendo mucho para ayudar a una completa extraña.

translation.en: Oh, Hope, I thought you knew me better than that.
Jack, I've known you a long time.
translation.es: Jack, te conozco desde hace mucho.

translation.en: If Mel was short for Melvin, we wouldn't be having this conversation.
translation.es: Si Mel fuera el apodo de un Melvin, no tendríamos esta conversación.

translation.en: I believe Hope has some good news for you.
translation.es: Creo que Hope tiene buenas noticias para ti.

translation.en: I'll put you up at the Fitches' while I figure out what to do with the cabin.
translation.es: Irás al Fitches mientras resuelvo lo de la cabaña.

translation.en: The place with the handsy husband?
Did I say that?
You know, I can fight my own battles.
Never turn down help when deep in a foxhole.
translation.es: Nunca rechaces la ayuda cuando la necesitas.

translation.en: How about a show of Virgin River hospitality?
translation.es: ¿Qué tal una muestra de la hospitalidad de Virgin River?

translation.en: Why don't I take you on a tour tomorrow?
translation.es: ¿Y si te llevo de paseo mañana?

translation.en: Okay, tell you what.
I'm gonna be at the river at seven a.m.
translation.es: Voy a estar en el río a las 7:00 a. m.

translation.en: If you want to join me,
I'll be there.
Hey. Uh, so, should I just pull up a chart and grab a patient?
translation.es: Hola. ¿Traigo una hoja clínica y recibo a un paciente?

translation.en: - No. - No?
No. Until I can confirm that you are competent, no patients.
translation.es: No. Hasta que compruebe que eres competente, nada de pacientes.

translation.en: Well, how can you confirm my competency if I can't see any patients?
translation.es: ¿Cómo lo comprobará si no puedo atender ningún paciente?

translation.en: Chitchat is over. I've got a waitin' room full of people.
translation.es: La charla se acabó. Tengo una sala de espera con gente.

translation.en: - Welcome. - Hi.
Oh, I am sorry that my husband isn't here to greet you as well.
translation.es: Lamento que mi esposo no esté para saludarte.

translation.en: - Oh... - He's doing a supply run in Grace Valley.
translation.es: Está comprando suministros en Grace Valley.

translation.en: We only have one room left, and, uh... I'm nervous that you won't like it.
translation.es: Solo nos queda un cuarto, y me pone nerviosa que no te guste.

translation.en: Hope told me that you're very picky.
translation.es: Hope me dijo que eres exigente.

translation.en: Yeah.
- Come take a look. - Okay.
- After you. - Thank you.
Boy, you picked the wrong place to rob.
Get your hands up.
Now turn around. Slowly.
Come on.
Hey, man.
Brady!
Bro, what are you doing in here, man?
I was leaving you a note. Wanted to let you know I was okay.
translation.es: Te dejaba una nota para avisarte que estoy bien.

translation.en: How the hell did you get in here?
Come on. I know where you keep the spare key.
translation.es: Vamos. Sé dónde guardas el duplicado de la llave.

translation.en: Listen, I-- I've got plans this morning.
translation.es: Tengo algo que hacer esta mañana.

translation.en: But why don't you go get something to eat, and then go up to my room,
translation.es: Pero ¿por qué no comes algo y luego vas a mi cuarto,

translation.en: grab some sleep, and then clean yourself up, okay?
translation.es: duermes un poco y te das un baño?

translation.en: All right.
Long time.
Welcome back.
Thanks, man.
Yeah.
Hey!
Hey.
Are you coming up, or am I coming down?
- You're comin' down here. - Okay.
Oh, I see you got a coffee.
Yeah. Paige's bakery truck.
translation.es: Sí. La panadería sobre ruedas de Paige.

translation.en: You could have mentioned it.
- I believe in self- discovery. - Ah.
- And practicality. - Ah!
Yeah.
- No, thank you. - No, no, no. I insist.
Where are we going?
I cleared your morning with Doc.
translation.es: No te preocupes. Te liberé la mañana con Doc.

translation.en: You cleared my morning.
Well, there's no cell reception out here,
so I figured you wouldn't want to give Doc any more ammunition by being late, so...
translation.es: y pensé que no querrías hacer enojar más a Doc por llegar tarde...

translation.en: - Wow. - But let me help you.
No, no. I don't need your assistance, okay?
Okay. I'm sorry I called Doc for you. It won't happen again.
translation.es: Bien. Lamento haber hecho eso. No volverá a pasar.

translation.en: Now, you wanna put your hand on my shoulder?
Okay, now step.
And... other one.
Step.
Okay.
- All right. We can leave this here. - Wait.
No. No, no, no. My whole life is in that bag.
translation.es: No. Toda mi vida está ahí.

translation.en: Oh, look, no one's gonna take it.
- Hm? - Because no one's here.
- Trust me? - Hm.
Mm. Hey, thank you.
- Uh... How much further? - We're almost there.
It's not even the best part.
translation.es: Y eso no es lo mejor.

translation.en: Eagles.
Here.
This is their favorite spot.
Mine too.
They're incredible. Huh.
Yeah.
So, what's next?
Nothin'.
Here.
Oh, thank you.
Yeah.
I think I can actually hear my heart beating.
translation.es: Creo que puedo oír los latidos de mi corazón.

translation.en: In peace, nothing so becomes a man... Or woman...
translation.es: En la paz, no hay nada que nos haga hombres o mujeres...

translation.en: - ...as modest stillness. - Shakespeare?
- Mm. - You an English major?
No, I never went to college.
translation.es: No, nunca fui a la universidad.

translation.en: But in my 20s, I loved to read while drinkin', so it kind of all evens out.
translation.es: De joven, me gustaba leer mientras bebía, así que todo se equilibra.

translation.en: - Is that hunters? - Yeah, could be.
Could be somethin' else.
There's a lot of illegal pot fields outside of Virgin River.
translation.es: Hay muchos campos de marihuana ilegal cerca de Virgin River.

translation.en: But it's legal now.
Yeah. It doesn't stop the illegal growers from doin' business.
translation.es: Sí. Eso no evita que los productores ilegales hagan negocios.

translation.en: Cross them, and things can turn dangerous.
translation.es: Si te los cruzas, puede ser peligroso.

translation.en: I used to work in the, uh... ER Level One Trauma Center,
translation.es: Yo trabajaba en un centro de trauma nivel uno de urgencias,

translation.en: so I've seen my fair share of what dangerous can do.
translation.es: así que he visto cosas peligrosas.

translation.en: ER, huh?
Sounds like an intense job.
Yeah, you could say that.
But I'm sure owning a bar has its challenges.
translation.es: Pero manejar un bar debe tener sus desafíos.

translation.en: Piece of cake, compared to my time in the service.
translation.es: Nada comparado con mis días en el ejército.

translation.en: Marine. Joined up right out of high school.
translation.es: Fui marine. Me enrolé al terminar la secundaria.

translation.en: Spent 20- plus years, mostly in the Middle East.
translation.es: Serví más de 20 años, sobre todo en Medio Oriente.

translation.en: Preacher was with me. And Brady. You haven't met him yet.
translation.es: Con Preacher. Y Brady, aún no lo conoces.

translation.en: Do you miss it?
Yes and no.
I had, um...
People who... depended on me.
And Virgin River, well, it's, uh...
it's a utopia, compared to a war zone.
translation.es: Es una utopía, si se compara con una zona de guerra.

translation.en: - Oh, here. - Oh...
- Aah. - Thank you.
You're welcome.
Thanks for this morning.
It was my pleasure.
Well, I'll see you around.
Yeah, you will.
- See ya. - Bye.
Hello?
Doc?
Is Doc here?
Hi, there. No, no, he's not in right now.
translation.es: ¡Hola! No, no está en este momento.

translation.en: He'll be back soon.
I'll wait.
Uh... I'm the new nurse practitioner. Maybe I can help you.
translation.es: Soy la nueva enfermera. Quizá pueda ayudarte.

translation.en: Uh... Oh, I'll wait for Doc.
- Um... When are you due? - Ooh...
Any day now.
- - It's okay.
Okay. I think I should take a look at you. I don't know when the doctor'll be back.
translation.es: Bien, voy a revisarte porque no sé cuándo volverá el doctor.

translation.en: - Okay? - Okay.
- Okay. Can you stand? - Okay.
Uh... Yeah.
- Yeah. - It's okay. Just take a breath.
- Ready? One, two, three. Up. - Okay.
There you go.
It's okay. You're gonna be just fine.
- Okay? - Okay.
- What's your name? - Polly.
- Polly Fishburn. - Polly Fishburn.
My name's Mel.
And I'm gonna take really good care of you, okay?
translation.es: Y voy a cuidarte muy bien, ¿sí?

translation.en: Okay.
You're gonna be just fine now. Can you get up on this table?
translation.es: Estarás bien. ¿Puedes subir a esta mesa?

translation.en: - Yeah.  - Got it?
- You got it. You got it. -
I've gone through last night's receipts twice.
translation.es: Revisé dos veces los recibos de anoche.

translation.en: - Mm- hm? - The cash box is light.
I advanced Ricky a week to prep the McCrea cabin for some maintenance. I--
translation.es: ¿Sabes qué? Le adelanté una semana a Ricky para que arregle la cabaña McCrea.

translation.en: I thought I logged that. Must have forgotten.
Oh, look who's back in town...
Brady.
So, how long before you disappear again?
I told him he could stay as long as he wants.
translation.es: Le dije que se quedara cuanto quisiera.

translation.en: I'm gonna head to Clear River. Run some errands. Catch you in a bit.
translation.es: Voy a Clear River, tengo cosas que hacer. Nos vemos luego.

translation.en: Yeah.
Uh, I left...
a lot of kids behind who I couldn't help.
translation.es: ...a muchos chicos a los que no pude ayudar.

translation.en: I can help Brady, okay? I'm not turning my back on him.
translation.es: Pero ayudaré a Brady, ¿sí? No le daré la espalda.

translation.en: Well, then, you may wanna change the locks on the office door.
translation.es: Te conviene cambiar las cerraduras de la oficina.

translation.en: Or you may be advancing Ricky a whole lot more than a week's pay.
translation.es: O terminarás adelantándole a Ricky mucho más que el pago de una semana.

translation.en: What is goin' on?
- I'm with a patient. - No, I--
I'm almost done. I'll be right out.
Is everything okay?
You're doing fine. Your baby is doing fine, okay?
translation.es: Lo estás haciendo bien. Tu bebé está bien, ¿sí?

translation.en: You're just having... some Braxton Hicks.
translation.es: Solo tienes contracciones de Braxton Hicks.

translation.en: - Oh. - False labor pains.
- - They don't feel false though, do they?
- No.  - No.
Uh... Why don't you just lay here and rest,
and I'll go call your husband to come pick you up, okay?
translation.es: Llamaré a tu esposo para que venga por ti, ¿sí?

translation.en: Okay.
Thanks, Mel.
You're very welcome.
- Who said you could give her an exam? - I was just doing my job.
translation.es: ¿Quién te dio permiso? Solo hice mi trabajo.

translation.en: This is my practice. My name is on that door.
translation.es: Es mi consultorio. Mi nombre está en la puerta.

translation.en: You do not work with a patient unless you have my permission.
translation.es: No puedes trabajar con ningún paciente sin mi permiso.

translation.en: Polly was having Braxton Hicks.
I had to examine her to make sure that she wasn't in premature labor.
translation.es: La examiné para descartar un parto prematuro.

translation.en: Did you know there's protein in her urine?
translation.es: ¿Sabía que hay proteínas en su orina?

translation.en: Don't lecture me about my patient.
translation.es: No me des lecciones sobre mi paciente.

translation.en: Well, it's not in her chart. - I don't put everything in the chart. - Uh- huh.
translation.es: - No está en su hoja clínica. - No registro todo en la hoja.

translation.en: - Okay, well, where do you put it? - Right here.
And if you're not here to tell me what's not in the chart?
translation.es: ¿Y si no está aquí para decirme qué falta en la hoja?

translation.en: My dear, I'm not just old, I'm old- school.
translation.es: Querida, además de viejo, soy chapado a la antigua.

translation.en: And in my day, a nurse would never, never question
translation.es: En mi época, una enfermera nunca cuestionaba los métodos

translation.en: the methods of a supervising physician.
translation.es: En mi época, una enfermera nunca cuestionaba los métodos de un médico supervisor.

translation.en: A nurse would know her place.
Well, I hope you'll join me in the 21st century.
translation.es: Bueno, espero que venga al siglo XXI.

translation.en: And your point is?
This time it was false labor, but what about the next Polly or whoever?
translation.es: Esta vez fue un parto falso, pero ¿y la próxima Polly o quien sea?

translation.en: Wh-- Do you want me to just stand by and watch someone bleed out if you're not here?
translation.es: ¿Quiere que me cruce de brazos si alguien se desangra en su ausencia?

translation.en: You should have called me.
I had things under control.
These patients, they are like my family.
translation.es: Estos pacientes son como mi familia.

translation.en: And I cannot trust you with them unless I know for sure you're not gonna hurt someone.
translation.es: Y no puedo confiártelos hasta asegurarme de que no los lastimarás.

translation.en: So, if I can't do what I was hired to do, what is it that you want me to do?
translation.es: Si no puedo hacer el trabajo para el que me contrataron, ¿qué hago?

translation.en: Well, straighten up the office.
File things. Uh-- Keep the coffee pot full.
translation.es: Archivar cosas. Mantener la cafetera llena.

translation.en: I like mine black and fresh.
translation.es: Me gusta el café negro y fresco.

translation.en: Hello, Polly.
He's refusing to let me do my job.
translation.es: No me deja hacer mi trabajo.

translation.en: - Give it time. - No, no, no, no, no.
This is not about time.
Okay, good medicine is about teamwork, and he doesn't want me on his team.
translation.es: La medicina requiere trabajo en equipo, y él no me quiere en el suyo.

translation.en: He'll come around.
He is rude, he is demeaning,
and he's a big- time chauvinist.
The man's got his quirks, I'll give you that.
It's obvious that he needs somebody, but it's not gonna work like this, okay?
translation.es: Es obvio que necesita a alguien, pero esto no va a funcionar.

translation.en: It needs to be his idea, or he's never gonna accept it.
translation.es: Si no es por iniciativa propia, nunca lo aceptará.

translation.en: My grandfather was just like him.
So, you understand. Yeah, and he's never gonna change.
translation.es: - Entonces lo entiendes. - Sí, y nunca cambiará.

translation.en: Look, Hope, the bottom line is that this is not what I signed up for.
translation.es: Escucha, Hope, lo cierto es que no vine aquí para esto.

translation.en: Join the club, sweetheart.
Life rarely gives us what we want.
translation.es: La vida rara vez nos da lo que queremos.

translation.en: Okay... I didn't join a club, okay? I took a job.
translation.es: No estoy en un club, ¿sí? Acepté un trabajo.

translation.en: I'm sorry, I have to give you notice.
translation.es: Lo siento, pero voy a renunciar.

translation.en: I'll give you time to find someone, but you need to start looking now.
translation.es: Te daré tiempo para buscar un reemplazo, pero debes empezar ya.

translation.en: She's so beautiful.
- And I saw my reflection - So, where's Bill?
- In the snow- covered hills - Work.
Auntie Mel.
- Till the landslide brought me down - You make beautiful babies.
So, when are you two gonna make me an aunt?
- What is love? - We're working on it.
- Can the child - Work harder.
- Rise above? - Okay.
- You know I rarely agree with your sister. - Can I sail
translation.es: Casi nunca coincido con tu hermana.

translation.en: - Ocean tides? - She's right.
- Can I handle the seasons - I have to run. Sorry.
Hey, Mel.
Jack?
- Well, maybe - You better take a look at this.
- Well, maybe - Jesus.
I'm pretty sure that's not Jesus.
